are not present.</s><s>Fatty acids are predominantly iso- and anteiso-branched.</s><s>This genus belongs to the family <em>Microbacteriaceae</em> of the phylum <em>Actinobacteria</em>.</s><s>The type species is <em>Microcella putealis</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>